name: "Take my hand #1" by Cinthia Ponce
description: Time is an eraser, it removes the burn, it allows you to heal, it forgets some of the things that are best forgotten; but some things, some people stay with you always. I believe in angels, not the ones with wings and a halo, the ones that don't look like angels. They are in disguise. Sometimes it is hard to know who is the saved and who is the savior. Take my hand and let's walk this path together no matter what.
